h=d640d018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=21403ddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"da7ab04492c1723732410653ac30ea68115c453a","tid":1512770,"uid":13076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owra9gJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fowra9gJ.png&h=787f30ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然聯合國係冇牙老虎<br />\n<br />\n但係曾偉雄嘅兩句：「你哋冇做錯到」<br />\n<br />\n「香港警察一見到暴力就逃跑，係咪大家想見到？我唔希望道歉成為一種風土病&hellip;&hellip;（警方）履行職責係咪應該道歉？相信大家都好清楚。」<br />\n<br />\n縱容香港警察日益橫蠻無理嘅就係佢<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲簽名！只係撐萬幾個名！<br />\n今日係最後機會！<br />\n<br />\n只需要簡單嘅姓名同埋email"},{"pid":"e8c8a4a2dd6e318875a1f8b9d248a47c241631e8","tid":1512770,"uid":13076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=d3b9502f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions</a>"},{"pid":"29c9b17481fb05c65d815b681caabe67a8874c5b","tid":1512770,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"屌，比班支那仔搞壞左個網，今日先收到email"},{"pid":"26c53e4a67e08c3ccc71debccab8f44f41e3d3d0","tid":1512770,"uid":260914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"大家快啲check email, 好多人開始收到了"},{"pid":"7e1088f2